metadata.name: Odyssey
metadata.description:
MAYA is building the world's finest NFT members’ club. Token holders will have access to the speakeasy as well as exclusive culinary, cultural and social experiences around the world. 

Located in the heart of downtown Montreal, Maya’s speakeasy will consist of an ethereal lounge with craft cocktails, premium liquors and elevated Thai cuisine. 

The NFT artwork, which is inspired by Thai Gods and Deities, was created by artist Suyeong Lee.
